                <section>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom:1rem;">How Does Text Become Bits?</h3>
                    <div class="question-box">
                        <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Step 1:</strong> Look up the code point for each character.</p>
                        <p class="small-text">Example: 'A' = 65 (ASCII) = U+0041 (Unicode).</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom:1rem;">How Does Text Become Bits?</h3>
